    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bolide is an arcade roguelike where you survive waves in space to unlock new skills! Completing waves earns you skill points, which are spent on a variety of skills! <strong>With tons possible skill combinations, 40+ skills, 10 modes, 500+ customization options, lots of modifiers, and more, every game will be unique!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>40+ Unique Skills! </strong>Create new skill combinations every game! The possibilities are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 Unique Game Modes!</strong> Including Hardcore, Limited Ammo, Time Attack, Collector, and more, there's something for every mood. Plus, customize gameplay with modifiers, so it's as easy or hard as you'd like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 500 Customization Options!</strong> Unlock new animated ships and customize your ship's color and supercharged status. Also, unlock new bullets, customize bullets, and supercharge them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge Waves. </strong>Hard waves with unique modifiers that will make you want to rage. (These can be disabled in settings).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30+ Steam Achievements and 20+ Steam Stats!</strong> Go for the gold!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully customizable keybinds.</strong> You can even bind multiple (or all) controls to a single key.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessibility features</strong> including an option for a simplified font, the ability to disable challenge waves, and more, so everyone can enjoy Bolide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Amazing music</strong> by the award-winning composer Andrew Piland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cloud Saves</strong> and more! Start Your Journey Today!</p>",
